<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Personal Portfolio</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS (light/dark aware) -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons (for theme toggle & hamburger) -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/CSS/style_porto.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- fixed navbar, semi‚Äëtransparent, toggle on right, theme toggle button -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-custom fixed-top py-2">
      <div class="container-fluid px-4">
        <!-- left side: brand SE (you can also put logo) -->
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#">
          <div
            class="position-relative, rounded"
            style="width: 50px; height: 40px; overflow: hidden;"
          >
            <!-- If logo image exists, show it -->
            <img
              src="../assets/Uploads/Pic/6.png"
              alt="Logo"
              class="logo-image"
            />
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- This group will contain theme toggle and 'Let's Talk / Download CV' on desktop, 
           on mobile toggle remains far right -->
        <div class="d-flex ms-auto order-md-3 align-items-center">
          <!-- Dark/light mode toggle button (sun/moon) -->
          <button class="btn theme-toggle me-2" id="themeToggleBtn">
            <i class="bi bi-sun-fill"></i>
          </button>

          <!-- 'Let's Talk' & 'Download CV' (visible on desktop, on mobile inside collapse) -->
          <div class="d-none d-md-flex align-items-center">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-turquoise me-2"><i
                class="bi bi-chat-dots me-1"
              ></i>Let's Talk</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-turquoise"><i
                class="bi bi-download me-1"
              ></i>Download CV</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- navbar toggler (hamburger) ‚Äì must be after the group above to stay most right -->
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler border-0"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarMain"
          aria-controls="navbarMain"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <!-- collapse + mobile menu items (Tech Stack, Experience, Projects) -->
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarMain">
          <!-- main menu ‚Äì centered on desktop, stacked on mobile -->
          <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto mb-2 mb-md-0 text-center">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#"><i
                  class="bi bi-stack me-1"
                ></i>Tech&nbsp;Stack</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#"><i
                  class="bi bi-briefcase me-1"
                ></i>Experience</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#"><i
                  class="bi bi-kanban me-1"
                ></i>Projects</a></li>
          </ul>
          <!-- mobile-only action buttons (Let's Talk + Download CV) visible inside collapse -->
          <div class="d-md-none text-center mt-3 pb-2">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-turquoise me-2"><i
                class="bi bi-chat-dots"
              ></i>
              Let's Talk</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-turquoise"><i
                class="bi bi-download"
              ></i>
              Download CV</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /container-fluid -->
    </nav>

    <!-- dummy page content to demonstrate scroll, fixed behavior & color palette -->
    <main class="container" style="max-width: 1000px;">
      <div class="demo-content my-5 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="mb-4"><i
            class="bi bi-palette me-2"
            style="color: #40e0d0;"
          ></i>
          turquoise & light‚Äëgreen palette</h2>
        <p>‚ú® Fixed navbar ‚Ä¢ semi‚Äëtransparent body ‚Ä¢ toggle always on right in
          mobile ‚Ä¢ dark/light switch works</p>
        <p>‚¨áÔ∏è scroll down ‚Äì navbar stays on top. Try resize to mobile width; the
          hamburger icon stays on the far right. Theme toggle button is placed
          right before hamburger (visible even on mobile). On narrow screens,
          'Let's Talk' & 'Download CV' move inside the collapsible menu.</p>
        <div class="row mt-4">
          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3"><span
              class="badge bg-turquoise p-3 w-100"
              style="background:#40e0d0; color:#01443d;"
            >turquoise #40E0D0</span></div>
          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3"><span
              class="badge p-3 w-100"
              style="background:#90ee90; color:#01443d;"
            >light-green #90EE90</span></div>
          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3"><span
              class="badge p-3 w-100"
              style="background:#2e8b57; color:white;"
            >sea-green #2E8B57</span></div>
          <div class="col-6 col-md-3 mb-3"><span
              class="badge p-3 w-100"
              style="background:#66cdaa; color:#01443d;"
            >medium aquamarine</span></div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4">üëâ scroll down and notice the fixed navbar,
          semi‚Äëtransparent with blur. Click the
          <i class="bi bi-sun"></i>
          /
          <i class="bi bi-moon-stars"></i>
          button to toggle dark mode (light/dark derived from
          turquoise/light-green).</p>
      </div>
      <!-- extra lines for scroll -->
      <div style="height: 700px;">
        <div
          class="card border-0 shadow p-4"
          style="background: rgba(144,238,144,0.1);"
        >
          <h5>More content ‚Üí shows fixed navbar</h5>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
            Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada
            fames ac turpis egestas. Donec tincidunt lectus eu fringilla
            faucibus. Nullam vitae nisi eu purus feugiat sodales. Praesent non
            ipsum eget leo ullamcorper interdum.</p>
          <p><i class="bi bi-droplet me-1" style="color:#40e0d0;"></i>
            Turquoise transparency remains.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS for collapse and toggles -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    ></script>
    <script src="../assets/JS/portofolio.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>